data.description: Love a peaceful lake view? This charming all-brick home is calling your name! Nestled on the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, this 4 bedroom 2 and 1/2  bath home offers plenty of space and privacy. A sprawling open kitchen features upgraded appliances and quartz countertops, perfect for entertaining friends and family. Cozy up by the fireplace in the family room or move to the bar area for an after dinner drink - you'll be amazed by all of the possibilities this house has to offer! And don't forget about that amazing private lake view from your stunning deck - it's truly a sight to behold. Don't miss out on this once-in-a-lifetime opportunity, come check it out today!
